OL,6,FMark Drakeford said he will
OL,7,F"absolutely not" be a backseat driver
OL,8,Fto his successor when he steps down as
OL,9,FWales' First Minister.
OL,11,FAhead of Mr Drakeford relinquishing
OL,12,FWelsh politics' top job, he sat down
OL,13,Fwith ITV Wales' Political Editor
OL,14,FAdrian Masters.
OL,16,FWhen asked if he will be a backseat
OL,17,Fdriver to his successor, Mr Drakeford
OL,18,Fresponded: "Absolutely not. I'm very
OL,19,Fdetermined that the new First Minister
OL,20,Fwill be able to get on with the job,
OL,21,Fdo it in there way.
