OL,4,Cbut doesn't rule out being a rebel
OL,6,F"I'm looking forward to being on the
OL,7,Fback benches and to have a bit of
OL,8,Ffreedom to think about and talk about
OL,9,Fsome of the things that you can't
OL,10,Falways rehearse when you're within the
OL,11,Fconfines of being First Minister and
OL,12,Fto support them in the difficult job
OL,13,Fthey will do."
