OL,6,FHe was then asked if he was planning
OL,7,Fon being a rebel, to which Mr
OL,8,FDrakeford said: "I'm not planning to
OL,9,Fbe a rebel particularly but I'm
OL,10,Flooking forward to a chance to say
OL,11,Fsome things that are not as easy to
OL,12,Fsay when you're confined by the
OL,13,Fresponsibilities that you have as
OL,14,FFirst Minister."
OL,16,FA recent ITV Wales/YouGov BarnCymru
OL,17,Fpoll showed 's popularity with the
OL,18,FWelsh public is at an 18-month low as
OL,19,Fmore than half of respondents (56%)
OL,20,Fbelieve he is doing a bad job of being
OL,21,FFirst Minister.
