OL,6,FWhen asked if he is disappointed by
OL,7,Fthat, Mr Drakeford said: "I've never
OL,8,Fmade a single decision that I've made
OL,9,Fwhen I've been First Minister on the
OL,10,Fbasis that it would make me more or
OL,11,Fless popular.
OL,13,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,14,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,15,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,16,Fdominating the political agenda...
