OL,6,F"It's nice when it does, but it's not
OL,7,Fthe reason I do things. The decision's
OL,8,FI've tried to make during the five
OL,9,Fyears I've been here are the difficult
OL,10,Fdecisions, the long term decisions
OL,11,Fthat may not be popular in the here
OL,12,Fand now, but lay down the foundations
OL,13,Ffor a more successful country in the
OL,14,Ffuture."
