OL,6,FMr Drakeford had previously ruled out
OL,7,Fa peerage and said: "I myself don't
OL,8,Fhave an interest in going to an
OL,9,Funelected House of Lords. It stands
OL,10,Ffor everything that I don't believe
OL,11,Fin."
OL,13,FHowever, he said he would consider it
OL,14,Fin a reformed House of Lords.
