OL,6,F"If a Labour Government is serious
OL,7,Fabout reforming the House of Lords, to
OL,8,Fuse the prescriptions in the Gordon
OL,9,FBrown report, to turn it into a forum
OL,10,Ffor the nations and the regions,
OL,11,Felected by people who live in the
OL,12,Fnations and the regions, then that is
OL,13,Fa prospect I would be interested to
OL,14,Fthink about."
